gitleaks is strongly recommended but not required. Three scan layers
skip gracefully when absent. gitleaks v8.30 scans notes by default via
git log --all. stdin mode broken — use dir with tmpfile.

Tested by: test-gitleaks.sh (16 assertions). Validates: inline scan blocks
secrets in note body/title, pre-commit blocks staged secrets, pre-push
blocks secrets in notes refs, clean content passes all layers.
